# Sponsor site 
this is a simple example of how to use [`chargily-epay-django`](https://pypi.org/project/chargily-epay-django/) plugin 

## Documentation
you can read documentation from [here](dev.codingdz.com/chargily-epay-django/)

## SETUP
Go to `settings.py` and configure the following variables
- [CHARGILY_API_KEY](http://dev.codingdz.com/chargily-epay-django/settings/#chargily_api_key)
- [CHARGILY_SECRET_KEY](http://dev.codingdz.com/chargily-epay-django/settings/#chargily_secret_key)
- [CHARGILY_FAKE_DOMAIN](http://dev.codingdz.com/chargily-epay-django/settings/#chargily_fake_domain)
- [CHARGILY_SITE](http://dev.codingdz.com/chargily-epay-django/settings/#chargily_site)

